edValue.getValue()).isEqualTo(expectedValue.getValue());\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1259, "output": 605, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29000, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778104694813, "responseId": "resp_0d702499bc0101000169fbb977904c81a3862457fe5790efbc"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_FK9dWdj3GwPqdTYB9wirlH9W|fc_0d702499bc0101000169fbb97b336081a3b6f80ff0965f7e22", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1161 bytes to tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcutil-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcutil_jdk15to18/OpaqueAnonymous1Test.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778104701447}]}
